3rdparty/
apps/
build/
cmake/
modules/
platforms/
samples/
doc/
CMakeLists.txt
SECURITY.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
*.md
!README.md
!INSTALL.md
!SETUP_GUIDE.md
!TROUBLESHOOTING.md
EOF